24 ambulance transport, including transport for a municipal fire or police department or other government entity.
25 (b) The term does not include:
26 (i) an entity that exclusively provides air ambulance services; or
27 (ii) an entity operated by the United States, an Indian tribe, or any facility authorized under the
28 Indian Health Care Improvement Act; or
