24 NEW SECTION. Section 5. Reporting and collection of assessment fee. (1) On or before March
25 31 JUNE 30 each year, an ambulance provider shall file with the department a report of its net operating revenue
26 received during the previous calendar year. The report must be:
27 (a) in the form prescribed by the department; and
28 (b) accompanied by a payment in an amount equal to the assessment fee required to be paid
